info.name: Palak Khichdi Pop
info.description: Serves 1 | A nutritious quick to eat snack/ meal blended with blanched spinach, lentil, rice, and chatpata mix for a savory, bite-sized treat.

info.name: Quinoa Khichdi Pop
info.description: Serves 1 | A wholesome snack combining protein-rich quinoa, lentils, rice, bell peppers and aromatic chatpata mix for a delicious, crunchy delight.

info.name: Multigrain Khichdi Pop
info.description: Serves 1 | A nutritious meal in a snack form made from a blend of grains, lentils, and crispy flavourful seed mix, offering a wholesome and flavourful bite.

info.name: Dal Palak Khichdi
info.description: Serves 1 | Relish this healthy and tasty khichdi prepared with spinach along with toor dal and rice. This easily digestible khichdi is all you need for a soulful day!Served with Pickle of the day.Allergen Information- Contains Dairy

info.name: Sabudana Khichdi
info.description: Serves 1 | Subtle and soft sabudana (sago) pearls tossed with curry leaves, chillies and roasted groundnuts- a delicious gluten-free meal. Served with Curd.[Soaked sabudana, Boiled Potato, Peanuts]Contains Sendha NamakAllergen Information- Contains Peanuts

info.name: Homely Vegetable Khichdi
info.description: Serves 1 | Special nutri-packed khichdi with the goodness of Dal & Veggies - a perfect light meal for the day! Served with special Papad Churi, Pickle & Gur.Served with Pickle of the dayAllergen Information: Contains Gluten & Dairy

info.name: Millet Curd Rice
info.description: Serves 1 | [Energy - 419kcal | Protein - 12gm] Tasty and creamy curd rice with the earthy flavour of foxtail millet for a nutritious yet light meal. Served with Pickle of the day.Allergen information: Contains Dairy, Peanuts & Seeds. *Served cold

info.name: Achari Khichdi
info.description: Serves 1 | Mighty khichdi with playful achari flavour & spices for a perfect joyride of tastefulness. Served with Pickle, Gur & Papad Churi.Served with Pickle of the dayAllergen Information- Contains Dairy

info.name: Palak Paneer Khichdi
info.description: Serves 1 | Enjoy this paneer filled khichdi with goodness of palak and rice.Served with Pickle of the dayAllergen informtion: Dairy, traces of mushroom and celery

info.name: Garlic Tadka Khichdi
info.description: Serves 1 | Classic yellow dal khichdi tempered with cumin, spices and finished with golden fried garlic and coriander.Served with Pickle of the day

info.name: Kathiyawadi Masala Khichdi
info.description: Serves 1 | Traditional masaledar kathiyawadi khichdi, cooked with mixed veggies, signature rajwadi masala and roasted peanuts. Served with a unique combination of achar, papad churi and gur.Served with Pickle of the dayAllergen information: Contains Peanuts, Dairy

info.name: High Protein Brown Rice Khichdi
info.description: Serves 1 | Gut friendly khichdi made with brown rice, dal, mix vegetables and aromatic spices with a touch of desi ghee, topped with spicy rolled oats- seed mix.Served with Pickle of the dayAllergen Information- Contains Dairy, Nuts & Seeds

info.name: High Protein Quinoa Khichdi
info.description: Serves 1 | pumpkin, beans, carrots and spices, topped with oar seed mix are the perfect addition to this ultra-nutritious khichdi. Served with Pickle of the day.Allergen Information- Contains Dairy, Nuts and Seeds

info.name: Iron Rich Daliya Khichdi
info.description: Serves 1 | Deliciously healthy khichdi made from moong dal & green peas, and garnished with spiced oat- seed mix for a hunger-fulfilling experience. Served with Pickle of the day.Allergen Information- Contains Dairy, Nut & Seed

info.name: Homestyle Dal Tadka Chawal
info.description: Serves 1 | Lentil gravy mixed with oil fried spices and herbs served with Jeera rice. A hearty meal for 1.

info.name: Dal Makhani Chawal
info.description:
Serves 1 | "A classic North Indian dish featuring creamy black lentils cooked with spices, served with aromatic steamed  jeera rice. A delightful and comforting combination.

Allergen Information- Contains Dairy"

info.name: Classic Rajma Chawal
info.description:
Serves 1 | Gently simmered red kidney beans cooked in onion tomato masala and aromatic Indian spices. Served with pickle.
Served with Pickle of the day

info.name: Brown Rice Masala Dal Khichdi
info.description: Serves 1 | [Energy - 596Cal | Protein - 19gm]A Gut friendly yummy khichdi made with brown rice, dal, mix vegetables with a touch of desi ghee. Served with Pickle of the dayAllergen Information- Contains Dairy

info.name: Quinoa Khichdi
info.description: Serves 1 | Anti-inflammatory and vegan, this yogic bowl of quinoa pumpkin khichdi is a crowd-pleaser. The mix of quinoa & dal, enhance the protein, added rice, pumpkin, beans and carrots are and spices are the perfect addition to this ultra-nutritious khichdi. Served with Pickle of the day. [Energy - 456Cal | Protein - 21gm] Allergen Information: Contains Peanuts, Seeds and traces of celery, mushroom.

info.name: Millet Curd Rice with Pomegranate
info.description: Serves 1 | Tasty and creamy curd rice with earthy flavour of foxtail millet for a nutritious yet light meal that's topped with pomegranate seeds.Served with Pickle of the day.Allergen information: Contains Dairy, Nuts & Seeds.*Served cold

info.name: Poha with Ratlami Sev
info.description: Serves 1 | Simple, soulful poha with onions and potatoes, topped with peanut masala. Served with Ratlami sev.Allergen information: Nuts

info.name: Poha with Sev
info.description: Serves 1 | A classic breakfast favourite prepared from flattened rice, onions, curry leaves and topped with peanut masala. Served with sev.Allergen Info - Contains Peanuts.

info.name: Fruit Pop Oatmeal
info.description: Serves 1 | "Our Fruit Pop Oatmeal bowl is the perfect way to refuel. A wholesome take on the overnight oats, we use nutritious rolled oats tossed with raisin, seeds, dates, basil seeds and seasonal fruits. It is sweetened with natural sugars like dates and jaggery.[Rolled Oats, Skim Milk, Basil Seeds, Pomegranate, Jaggery]Allergen Information: Contains Gluten, Dairy & Nuts.*Please note, the selection of fruits may vary from those pictured based on seasonality. Also, this item is served cold."

info.name: Mango Fruit Pop
info.description: Serves 1 | [Energy - 387Cal | Protein - 7gm] This vegan tropical fruit pop made with broken wheat, cashews, almonds sweetened with mango jaggery blend along with other fruits is sure to bring back the nostalgia of summers.Allergen information: Nuts, gluten.

info.name: Dal Makhani (420g)
info.description: Serves 1 | Rich and creamy Indian lentil dish made from black urad dal (black gram) and chana dal, simmered in a tomato-based gravy with butter and cream, resulting in a decadently flavorful and comforting dish. Allergen Information- Contains Dairy

info.name: Ghar Ki Dal (380g)
info.description: Serves 1 | Our homestyle Ghar ki Dal - a mix of high protein and easily digestible dals cooked in mild spices - that’s small on calories and big on taste, is now available in sharing portions too! Enjoy this simple yet delicious dal with rotis, parathas or both and don't forget to share the joy with your folks!

info.name: Bhindi Chana (360g)
info.description: Serves 1 | Ladies finger and black chana cooked with panchphoran and onion tomato masala comes in shareable portion for you to enjoy with either roti / paratha or rice.Allergen information: Seed

info.name: Steamed Rice (600g)
info.description: Serves 1 | A perfect companion waiting to be paired up and fill your tummy. Serves 2-3 folks.

info.name: Mango Pudding
info.description: Serves 1 | A delightful mango dessert made with ripe mango pulp, broken wheat, coconut milk and topped with nuts and pomegranate seeds. Perfect summery treat! Allergen Information- Contains Dairy, Gluten and Nuts

info.name: Chocolate Nutty Dates Pudding
info.description: Serves 1 | Be ready to go nuts over this delectable combination of chocolate, nuts and dates pudding with the chewy base of broken wheat.[Skim Milk, Dark Chocolate, Coconut Milk, Jaggery]Allergen information: Contains Gluten, Dairy & Nuts.

info.name: Badam Kheer
info.description: Serves 1 | Creamy rich and delicious keer with skimmed milk, rice, sweetened with jaggery and topped with roasted almonds.[Skim Milk, Rice, Jaggery, Roasted Almonds]Allergen information: Dairy, nuts

info.name: Badam Kheer (400gm)
info.description: Serves 1 | Creamy rich and delicious keer with skimmed milk, rice, sweetened with jaggery and topped with roasted almonds.[Skim Milk, Rice, Jaggery, Roasted Almonds]Allergen information: Dairy, nuts

info.name: Classic Masala Chaas
info.description: Serves 1 | Grab on the low calorie buttermilk with cooling properties and refresh yourself.Allergen information: Dairy"For immediate consumption"

info.name: Tender Coconut Water
info.description: Serves 1 | A refreshing natural tender coconut water for the day! This power-packed simple drink is full of fibre and electrolytes that switches you to a relaxing mode. Enjoy and de-stress yourself with every sip.Allergen Information: Nuts."For immediate consumption"

info.name: Jamun (200ml)
info.description: Serves 1 | [Energy - 96Cal] 100% Natural jamun smoothie with black salt. No added sugar, preservatives, or colour. Vegan-friendly and gluten-free. Anti-diabetic drink.

info.name: Mango (200ml)
info.description: Serves 1 | 100% Natural mango smoothie with pineapple. No added sugar, preservatives, or colour. Vegan-friendly and gluten-free. Great source of Vitamin C.

info.name: Sugarcane (200ml)
info.description: Serves 1 | [Energy - 90Cal] 100% Natural sugarcane juice with ginger and lemon. No added sugar, preservatives, or colour. Vegan-friendly and gluten-free. Great for hydration.

info.name: Aam ka Panna (200ml)
info.description: Serves 1 | 100% Natural aam ka panna. No added sugar, preservatives, or colour. Vegan-friendly and gluten-free. Great for immunity.

info.name: Melon Ice Tea
info.description: Serves 1 | Fusion of detoxing tea infused with the refreshing essence of melon, khandsari sugar and lime seasoning for a perfect revitalizing drink.

info.name: Peach Ice Tea
info.description: Serves 1 | A delightful blend of brewed tea decoction, peach extract, khandsari sugar, and lime seasoning for a rejuvenating & fruity experience.
